<HEADLINE>
FT  14 DEC 93 / People: Non-executive directors
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The Rt Hon Archie Hamilton MP at The WOODGATE FARMS DAIRY.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Companies:-
</XX>
